Wach mokor kuom Babulon


1  Wach mane Nyasaye onyiso e fweny kuom thimm man but nam e ma:

E fweny malichno nanenoe kalausi mager

kaa e thim man yo milambo, ma en piny ma ji oluoro.


2  Ne aneno kaka dala mandhogo ji, ondhogi.

Ne awinjo ka Nyasaye jiwo jo-Elam kod jo-Media

ni mondo odhi omonj Babulon kendo olwore,

mondo sungane orum.


3  Kane aneno fwenyno ne apuodora ka rem rama malit,

mana ka dhako ma muoch kayo.

Gik mane aneno kendo awinjo ne ogoya gi kibaji, mi adhier nono.


4  Dhoga nomoko kendo natetni ma ok anyal konyo

Ne asegeno ni abiro yueyo godhiambo, ka chieng’ opodho,

to kindeno nolokorena mana masira.


5  Bende naneno ka chiemo oseket piny, mi ochan kombe,

kendo ka jatend jo-Babulon chiemo kendo metho,

to e sano ne gipo ka oluonggi

mondo gimanre gi gigi mag lweny.


6  Ruoth Nyasaye nowachona kama:

“Ket jang’icho mondo ohul gik ma oneno.


7  Ka oneno geche lweny ka biro,

ma farese ariyo ariyo ywayo,

kaachiel gi joma oidho kenje kod ngamia,

to mondo orang ane maber gima timore.”


8  Bang’e jang’icho nokok niya,

“Jaduong’, asebet ka achung’ kar ng’icho

odiechieng’ gotieno duto pile,


9  

to koro echa aneno joidh farese ka biro,

kaachiel gi geche lweny ma farese ariyo ariyo ywayo.”

Eka nawinjo dwoko niya,

“Babulon osepodho!

Osepodho, kendo nyisechene manono osemuki moriere piny.”


10  Yaye, jothurwa ma jo-Israel,

ma osenyon ka kal minyono kidino,

asenyisou gik ma Ruoth Nyasaye Manyalo Gik Moko Duto ma Nyasach Israel owachona.

Wach mokor kuom Duma


11  Ma e wach mane Nyasaye oyiso e fweny kuom Duma:

Ne awinjo ng’ato ka luonga Seir.

Ne openjo niya, “In jang’icho koro en sa adi mar otieno?”


12  Ne adwoko niya,

“Piny chiegni ru, to obiro yuso kendo.

To kudwaro penjo kendo, to uduog ira.”

Wach mane okor kuom jo-Arabu


13  Ma e wach mane Nyasaye onyiso e fweny kuom jo-Arabu:

Un jo-Dedan ma bworo e thim gi jo-Arabu,


14  kod un joma odak Tema,

rwakuru joma oseringo, kumiyo chiemoo gi pi,


15  nikech giseringo lweny mager,

minegoe ji gi ligangla kod asere mabith.


16  Ruoth Nyasaye osewacho niya, “Kapok higa achiel orumo ngang’, to duong’ duto mar jo-Arabu ma Kedar notieki. 
17  Jo asere marateke maggi manok kende ema nodong’, nimar Ruoth Nyasaye ma Nyasach Israel ema owacho kamano.”

